quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"In the name of Allah, the Entirely Merciful, the Especially Merciful"
  1,2,"The praise belongs to God, the Guardian Evolver of all systems of knowledge"
  1,3,"The Merciful Benefactor, the Merciful Redeemer"
  1,4,Sole Judge on the Day of Judgement
  1,5,"We only worship You, and we beg for your assistance"
  1,6,Guide us on the straight path
  1,7,"The way of those on whom You bestow blessings, not those who incur your wrath, nor those who go astray"
